io.github.kensuke1984.kibrary.waveformdata

クラス BasicID

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.kensuke1984.kibrary.waveformdata.BasicID
  • 直系の既知のサブクラス:
    PartialID

    public class BasicID
extends java.lang.Object

    ID for observed and synthetic waveform

    This class is IMMUTABLE

    Double values will be rounded off to 3rd decimal places.
    (Those are stored as Float in the file)

    =Contents of information for one ID=
    If one is observed(true) or synthetic(false)
    Name of station
    Name of network
    Horizontal position of station (latitude longitude)
    Global CMT ID
    Component (ZRT)
    Period minimum and maximum
    Start time
    Number of points
    Sampling Hz
    If one is convoluted or observed, true
    Position of a waveform for the ID

    • コンストラクタの詳細

      • BasicID

        public BasicID(WaveformType waveFormType,
               double samplingHz,
               double startTime,
               int npts,
               Station station,
               GlobalCMTID globalCMTID,
               SACComponent sacComponent,
               double minPeriod,
               double maxPeriod,
               long startByte,
               boolean convolute,
               double... waveformData)
        パラメータ:
        waveFormType - Type of waveform data.
        samplingHz - [Hz] Sampling Hz.
        startTime - [s] start time of the time window.
        npts - Number of data points
        station - Information of station.
        globalCMTID - Event ID for the data.
        sacComponent - Component of the data.
        minPeriod - [s] minimum period of the applied filter if none, 0
        maxPeriod - [s] minimum period of the applied filter if none, Double.POSITIVE_INFINITY
        startByte - [byte] where the waveform data for this ID starts in the file
        convolute - If the data is convolute.
        waveformData - the waveform data for this ID.
